name: The Wavement (Cyst Shimmer)
description: Artist: Marcel Schwittlick (@schwittlick_) Custom algorithmic system. This software constantly generates new variations within the boundaries of the rules. An everlasting continuous animation exploring the mind. The infinitely changing movement is evolving into forms of the known and unreal. It is generated and edited live, exploring space in it's own limited form.  Created using Processing. 2011
